data.meta_description: Ernst Wilhelm Schubert was born on May 12, 1861, son of Johann Ernst Schubert and Johanne Christiana Eichler. He was married on January 24, 1889 in the Ev. Luth. Church of St. Michael Hahndorf, South Australia to Wilhelmine Henriette Schneemilch, they had 6 children. He died on April 11, 1929. This information is part of Family tree Thiele by John Janmaat on Genealogy Online.
